50
00:13:42.684 --> 00:13:48.633
Incoming livestream: A question is an interpretive sentence generally denoted by an inflection at the end, like this.

51
00:13:48.944 --> 00:14:03.644
Incoming livestream: A question differs from a statement in that a question requests information and a statement provides it. We prefer questions to statements, and if you frame your question as succinctly as possible within 30 seconds, we can get to as many people as possible. And we have the Slack, so please get on the Slack.

